para.verbatim:
Update the progress bar by advancing a specified number of steps, and optionally set the ``current_item`` for this new position.
:param n_steps: Number of steps to advance. :param current_item: Optional item to set as ``current_item`` for the updated position.
.. versionchanged:: 8.0 Added the ``current_item`` optional parameter.
.. versionchanged:: 8.0 Only render when the number of steps meets the ``update_min_steps`` threshold.
Return a generator which yields the items added to the bar during construction, and updates the progress bar *after* the yielded block returns.
